data.description: Adorable & seriously low maintenance condo offering 2 primary bedrooms with en-suites, AND a large bonus room (office/playroom). NEW LVP flooring throughout the 1st level, lots of storage space, pet friendly community, and amenities galore - 2 Resort-style swimming pools with cabanas, grilling stations, and wet bars; Private community center, playgrounds, 24/7 fitness center, community lakes, and beautifully landscaped walking trails.  Just about EVERYTHING is covered including all water, trash, & sewer!  Master insurance policy, front lawn & common areas are all professionally maintained! Spence Crossing offers the best of both worlds! Providing a private & peaceful atmosphere, yet is centrally located with quick & easy access to Town Center, Oceanfront, interstates, military bases, restaurants and shopping galore! No flood hazard required! Schedule your private showing today and check out the virtual tour, you will NOT be disappointed!
